{"tid":2079414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"笑咗，連登仔一見香港眾志支持BLM就屌咗先","createTime":"2020-06-25T19:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T03:53:27.000Z","uid":36775,"like":25,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8ed2880397c064cf6d75a533865d3fe44de93d80","tid":2079414,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T19:32:11.000Z","msg":"只有得連登侵粉覺得會影衰香港人姐<br />\n外國根本大部份人對BLM示威目的唔反感<br />\n只係割搶野班人<br />\n講到BLM咁十惡不赦咁<br />\n如果BLM咁臭朵外國啲大公司就唔會公開支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n眾志咪咁做咪當幫香港人做下PR<br />\n又無出聲支持人搶野<br />\n走去拎下道德高地又屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比班連登傻鳩侵粉打國際線<br />\n一定講到香港人pro trump<br />\n到時就真係臭朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明大部份人都係和平示威<br />\n係入夜後有班gangs借故發難<br />\n同有一班毛派左膠搞事<br />\n如果呢一少部份人搞事=全部人暴徒/活動變質唔應該支持<br />\n同樣logic外國都唔應該繼續支持香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開始和平示威，到後期有裝修同私了（相信大部份外國人都好難公開撐你私了同裝修）<br />\n唔通人地就話你示威變質就唔支持香港人爭取民主咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登仔本質上同藍屍無分別<br />\n見侵屌就根住一齊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同藍屍睇完星島、文匯大公社評就跟住一齊屌<br />\n最好笑覺得BLM會幫侵拎到分<br />\n明明平時記者會啲語氣同777一樣<br />\n更加證明班人根本就藍屍嚟<br />\n比人叫child登唔係無原因<br />\n預咗比班盲毛屌，歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f975bc0c1575324add96c20b54351895f51de6","tid":2079414,"uid":131282,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T19:38:05.000Z","msg":"敖狗咁夜都唔瞓既"},{"pid":"42eff852ee666b0da27578e4af2671f1ad732fc3","tid":2079414,"uid":36775,"like":9,"dislike":7,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c6f975bc0c1575324add96c20b54351895f51de6","tid":2079414,"uid":131282,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T19:38:05.000Z","msg":"敖狗咁夜都唔瞓既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T19:42:22.000Z","msg":"唔啱聽=敖狗<br />\n連燈仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f3ef9cdf111096df413e4bc0e6e3f18b970305","tid":2079414,"uid":36775,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T19:44:00.000Z","msg":"見到連燈仔打國際線會點柒法就想笑<br />\n實拍得住熱狗同青山派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0305301f3ff33a3dfcea893b67c13da15bc5cfc","tid":2079414,"uid":36775,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T19:54:25.000Z","msg":"連登傻鳩侵粉=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正常人=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：All in 侵，侵侵贏硬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔洗engage埋民主黨，買曬兩邊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：民主黨正左膠，奶共。民主黨上場molamola<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：萬一侵輸點算？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我唔知道，總之侵贏硬，侵侵好野，又撚狗黑白臉！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：死左膠，二毛，識唔識美國政治（下刪3000字）"},{"pid":"66c1c2d2855298a5758cc245d3ebb7d73d042ab6","tid":2079414,"uid":36775,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T19:55:58.000Z","msg":"等緊侵粉入嚟屌柒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\